[2;36m│[0m and resetting the cookie to empty list.                                      [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m The payloads I've tried include:                                             [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. `eval("dict(os.environ)")` with various encodings                         [2;36m│[0m
