[2;36m│[0m 5. `exec('import os; os.environ')`                                           [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 6. Causing exceptions to see error output                                    [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 7. Various pickle object structures                                          [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m All requests return the same normal HTTP 200 page with no environment        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m variable output visible.                                                     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m The issue seems to be that:                                                  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 1. The payload execution results aren't visible in the HTTP response         [2;36m│[0m
